title: Greenbank Restaurant
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Japanese, Take-out, Asian, Korean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A Korean-owned Japanese restaurant whose owner is open to suggestions. Vegans could get avocado rolls, the Greenland roll, and kampyo maki. Has brown, vegetable stir fry option, and a few meals/sides can be customized. Sells some food products for take home like soy sauce, brown rice, green tea with toasted brown rice.
